Exudate Absorbent Dressings are specialized medical dressings designed to effectively absorb and manage wound exudate. During the healing process, wounds can produce large volumes of fluid; if this fluid is not removed promptly it may lead to infection, delayed tissue repair or increased patient discomfort. By providing controlled fluid removal, these dressings promote a moist wound environment, reduce the risk of maceration, and improve overall patient quality of life.
